Generic single-database configuration with async support for NSG VisionAI Platform.

This Alembic environment is configured to work with:
- Async SQLAlchemy (asyncpg driver)
- PostgreSQL 16
- TimescaleDB extension
- pgvector extension

Usage:
  # Generate a new migration
  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"

  # Apply migrations
  alembic upgrade head

  # Rollback one migration
  alembic downgrade -1

  # Show current revision
  alembic current

  # Show migration history
  alembic history
